Comment: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:30.73,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Piros éjszaka is a hungarian word meaning, "Crimson Night"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:07.83,Default,Kukuri Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.63,Default,Kukuri Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.55,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.49,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yu... ka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.92,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.81,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.73,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean I can meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.77,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,...that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:30.74,EP-Title,Typeset,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8\fscx80\fscy80\fad(486,0)\t(0,1028,\blur0\fscx100\fscy100\shad3)\t(1029,1030,\bord0.1)\t(1653,3989,\shad12\blur5)\pos(625,514)}Crimson Night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.56,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:54.59,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.71,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.73,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I came looking for you because you disappeared, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.68,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you didn't return first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.51,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.39,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.36,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.91,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,The moon? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:17.69,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.92,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.58,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.89,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.10,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,my older sister ended her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.10,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Being brought up in an institution,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.98,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,my sister was my only family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't completely accept what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:46.80,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,and closed my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.62,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Only Yuka, who was from the same institution,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.13,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,had always smiled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.46,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,She had stayed close, and laughed for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.54,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuka weren't here, I wonder how I would've turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:05.48,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.96,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.30,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we return?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.46,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even so... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.82,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.77,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.50,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.39,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Tadashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.89,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you found Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was looking at the moon on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.06,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.99,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You two were up on the roof alone this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.95,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.55,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.69,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Some dazzling event had occured, right, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.24,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You have to send me a picture mail! Picture mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.79,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird delusions are you having, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.49,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Tadashi-kun! Kaori-chan, you're going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.35,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've made me get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:20.15,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You have woken up the real me inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.31,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.28,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "you"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.88,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,S-Strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:32.35,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Dang you! You must be the legendary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:37.33,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I don't talk much, if at all, with anyone other than Yuka, Tadashi and Kaori casually came up to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:42.19,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I'm with the cheerful twosome, my feelings naturally become calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:52.54,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're saying that today and tomorrow there's going to be an outlet sale at Ianith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.53,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What kinds of outlets are at Ianith?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.75,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.74,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Like western clothing or general goods-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.29,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Or indecent gravure photo shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.90,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, perverted Tadashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.78,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're going right now, so you wanna come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.85,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.91,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, you don't need to mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.28,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:33.37,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka was adopted by the Minase family the year she entered elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:38.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The married Minase couple, who had no children, warmly welcomed Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.32,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.02,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.44,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.68,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.43,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.00,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ianith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:09.71,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.31,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.38,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.63,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.10,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.53,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A black... moon....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.98,11eyes - Cell,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fax-0.21\fsp-1\pos(516,185)}\hOut of\NRange
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:00.96,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.26,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, what in the world's going on, hey!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.05,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I also don't know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.78,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.67,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's disappeared somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.13,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.89,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.38,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.83,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.91,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.37,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:50.32,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, let's go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:51.43,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,School?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.69,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a chance someone is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.67,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What is... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:03.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.52,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.25,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,We're... back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.08,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw a bad dream, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.44,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.96,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to pick you up, your door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:38.07,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something happened and I panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.44,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.19,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,When we came back yesterday, I was a bit dazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.75,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.81,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.72,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:52.62,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I was too scared to close my eyes... so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.30,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.34,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.75,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You were just sleeping, soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.93,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you jump to conclusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do remember, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.29,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Will it happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.72,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That... Crimson Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.64,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.14,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.49,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.63,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Walking to school together like a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.23,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.49,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.66,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens again, I will protect you, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.60,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.90,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.29,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.64,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.46,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.50,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,People will misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.59,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You made her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.89,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You made a girl cry in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.37,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.30,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:45.82,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.78,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:58.41,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let me introduce a transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.54,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\pos(697,221)}Shiori Momono
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.54,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fs33\pos(1085,184)}17 July
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.54,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fs23\c&H7C8872&\u1\pos(1046,391)}Duty\N{\u0}Teruna\NYatsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.54,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,This is Shiori Momono-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.50,Default,Tadashi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute! Moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:07.87,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Momono-san came back to Japan from Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.55,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Italy? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.60,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Momono-san, please introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.88,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.39,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.35,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\pos(697,221)}Shiori Momono
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.35,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fs33\pos(1085,184)}17 July
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.35,11eyes - Board,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fs23\c&H7C8872&\u1\pos(1046,391)}Duty\N{\u0}Teruna\NYatsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.09,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.11,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's your hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.26,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your house at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.29,Default,students,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in Kuino Shirohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.82,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
