Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.43,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Now first, what's your three sizes-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.56,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.63,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any interest in you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.43,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,So don't interfere with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:06.19,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
