Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.49,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:25.27,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I can walk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.31,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.45,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm lacking sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.67,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
