Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.76,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see? I've got a sick person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.62,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.66,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, playing princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.96,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just anemia, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:26.24,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Then, I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.91,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Satsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.37,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if you don't want to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.69,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I had it since birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.06,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minase...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun can't see through his right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:01.24,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, his irises have a different color so he wears the eye patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he... your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.89,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see. It's still in that stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.47,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you get some sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.68,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.39,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.11,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not too hard on your body, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:47.06,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ianith. We couldn't go yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.96,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,The outlet sale is until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:53.98,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.03,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:08.07,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right. Mother and Father said for you to come over sometime and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.58,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.85,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come over today when we return?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.86,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll come over another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.55,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, you always carry that but... what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:20.58,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Penzo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.51,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Penzo... san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.97,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Penzo-san is incredible, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.25,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.09,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.07,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I know right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.19,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... not go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.12,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.67,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:36.75,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right not having bought anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:41.67,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. If I'm with you, it's fun just looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.00,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good thing we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.57,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like the shock and insecurity from yesterday has worn off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.22,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,...but this smile isn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.49,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.49,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.19,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we... do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.35,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.83,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.04,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.82,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:10.99,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.65,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever that thing was doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:26.22,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Yuka to have painful thoughts anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:30.18,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it doesn't happen again, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.40,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:37.75,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if it were always like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.11,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.07,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru... kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.74,0:21:55.85,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:23.66,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.28,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.78,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why has Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:38.04,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.04,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.46,0:24:40.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Crystal Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.39,0:24:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.08,0:24:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is there an answer?
